steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"foa3m","text":"Prepare the 2X master mix (ul per sample):","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6bgrm","text":"- 2ul RT Buffer","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6dpj7","text":"- 0.8ul 25X dNTP Mix(100mM)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6mht0","text":"- 2ul Random primers","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fo9k7","text":"- 1ul Multiscribe Reverse Transcriptase","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ecqp8","text":"- 4.2ul Nuclease free water","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"41u4t","text":"Mix the 2X master mix (10ul) with the RNA samples (10ul) and mix by pippeting","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"achrd","text":"Centrifuge the plates to spin down all the reagents.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"e1b3n","text":"Program the thermal cycler to 25C for 10min 37C for 120 mintues 85C for 5 minutes and 4C until finished.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3rsqh","text":"Store the cDNA samples at -20C for short-term storage or -80C for long-term storage (years).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"391cc","text":"Take 0.5ug of RNA in a maximum of 10ul of sample volume","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
